headline.print_headline: Liverpool Rue Failure to Get Past Chelsea's Two Buses
headline.main: Liverpool Rue Failure to Get Past Chelsea's Two Buses

lead_paragraph: Liverpool coach Brendan Rodgers got his big break in football as an assistant to Jose Mourinho, but he will not be taking any lessons in how to win from his former mentor.
